window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Life can be good when your enemies think you're dead.</b></p> <p>But Wynne has traded one set of foes for another, and a hunter in old tech armor wants him for sinister purposes. Neither fully man or machine, it's up to this new bunker core to rise up against all odds, using his wits and technology to prevail against twisted animal-folk, shining mutants, and threats<i> literally</i> from out of this world....</p>"; 
